rows.label: tlk45400251_02_msg0001
rows.name:
I actually caught a glimpse of
Special Inquisitor Meleph recently!
In the flesh!

rows.label: tlk45400251_02_msg0003
rows.name:
She effortlessly toppled that villainous
boy to the ground and then launched
him high into the air!

rows.label: tlk45400251_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Then she rained attacks on him
while he was helpless to resist!

rows.label: tlk45400251_02_msg0005
rows.name:
So elegant... So refined...
It was like watching a master at work!

rows.label: tlk45400251_02_msg0006
rows.name: Huh? That's not how you remember it?

rows.label: tlk45400251_02_msg0007
rows.name:
Don't taint my memories... That's how
it looked to me from a distance!

rows.label: tlk45400251_02_msg0102
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]Wh-what should I say?! I can't breathe!
Am I dreaming? Is Meleph-sama really
standing right in front of me?!
